        <p>The Digital Scholarship Group (DSG) is an applied research and development group within the Northeastern University Library. DSG provides expertise, infrastructure, and strategic guidance for researchers and projects at Northeastern, and also works collaboratively to develop inter-institutional projects with groups like the Primary Source Cooperative. To learn more about, contact, or work with the DSG, you can visit our website at <a href="https://dsg.northeastern.edu/">dsg.northeastern.edu</a>.
